description._content: Title: Phare de L'ile Vierge Alternative Title: Virgin Island Lighthouse Creator: Unknown Date: 1883 Series: Tome Cinquieme: Phares et Balises Place: Plouguerneau, Finistere, France Description: The full title of the five-volume set is, Les travaux publics de la France par MM. F. Lucas et V. Fournie - Ed. Collignon - H. de Lagrene - Voisin Bey - E. Allard. Ouvrage publie sous les auspices de Ministere des travaux publics et sous la direction de M. Leonce Reynaud. This photograph is one of 50 plates in Public Works of France, Volume Five: Lighthouses and Beacons. Physical Description: 1 photographic print: collotype; 26 x 35 cm on 40 x 56 cm mount File: vault_folio_2_ta71_a4_1883_5_21_opt.jpg Rights: Please cite Southern Methodist University, Central University Libraries, DeGolyer Library when using this image file.
